				<h2 class="heading--2">Embracing a best-in-class scanning solution</h2>

				<p class="paragraph--2">To secure its network against potential threats, Visma has embraced the Enterprise TruRisk Platform to deliver in-depth security scans.</p>

				<p class="paragraph--2"><b><i>"We initially deployed Qualys Vulnerability Management to support a new operations model for cloud delivery, based on agile and DevOps methodologies,"</i></b> Holen recalls. <b><i>"The aim was to create a culture of security by making our development teams responsible both for writing secure code and—crucially—for deploying that code in secure environments.</i></b></p>

